trans-unit.source: Represents an item in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ListBox"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"></xref> control in an application that was upgraded from Visual Basic 6.0.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et element i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ListBox"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox"> </xref> kontroll i en applikasjon som ble oppgradert fra Visual Basic 6.0.

trans-unit.source: In Visual Basic 6.0, the `ListBox` and `ComboBox` controls use a `List` property to store list items and an `ItemData` property to optionally store an `Integer` associated with each list item.
trans-unit.target: I Visual Basic 6.0 den `ListBox` og `ComboBox` kontroller bruker en `List` til å lagre listeelementer og en `ItemData` til å lagre eventuelt en `Integer` som er forbundet med hvert listeelement.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox> controls use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox.Items%2A> property to store list items, and the `ItemData` property is no longer supported.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox>Kontroller bruker den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox.Items%2A>til å lagre listeelementer, og `ItemData` egenskapen støttes ikke lenger.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox.Items%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox>

trans-unit.source: When a Visual Basic 6.0 application is upgraded to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], the upgrade tools create a `ListBoxItem` class for each item in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox> control.
trans-unit.target: Når et program i Visual Basic 6.0 oppgraderes til [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/add/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], oppgradering verktøyene opprette en `ListBoxItem` klasse for hvert element i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox>eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ListBox>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.SetItemData%2A> and <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.GetItemData%2A> functions can then be used to enable any code that references the `ItemData` property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.SetItemData%2A>og <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.GetItemData%2A>funksjoner kan deretter brukes til å aktivere kode som refererer til den `ItemData` egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.GetItemData%2A> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.Support.SetItemData%2A>
